I would have to agree that the 41-50 pet is a huge asset.  Without it at level 50, you'll be sending green pets at people.  Tanks will completely ignore green pets, and I can cast through most green's attacks without even using quickcast.  Without the better pet, I wouldn't even bother using one. <P>With that said my first char in beta was a sorcerer.  After playing many levels with a pet, I decided I didn't want to have to rely on one in PVP.  I then started playing a Wizard.  After we were given the run speed buff I started looking more at other options for the Sorc class.  I switched back to Sorc and decided to try out the Body/Mind combo options.  I'm still planning to go 35 body, 34 mind(2nd to last ae mez).
